          <num>59-1-1309</num>
          <heading>Penalty may be waived, reduced, or compromised for reasonable cause.</heading>
          <content>
            <p>59-1-1309.
Penalty may be waived, reduced, or compromised for reasonable cause.
Upon making a record of its actions, and upon reasonable cause shown, the commission may waive, reduce, or compromise a penalty imposed by this part.
Enacted by Chapter
237
, 2006 General Session</p>
